      Things happen
   =20
 =20

Sam Bankman-Fried Makes His Last Stand. The heartland oil refiner fuelling =
 Carl Icahn=E2=80=99s empire. Trump Is Closer Than Ever to a Giant  Truth S=
ocial Payday. China Tells   Quants to Phase Out Strategy Blamed for Turmoil=
. U.S. Opens  UnitedHealth Antitrust Probe. Big investors grow nervous abou=
t  private credit boom. Measuring  Treasury Market Depth. Use profits from =
 frozen Russian assets to arm Ukraine, says Ursula von der Leyen. The Hail =
Mary Tactic to Pay Off Student Debt:  Sports Betting.=C2=A0
