ackground-color: #ccc;">is that</a> banks =E2=80=9Cwere saddled with billio=
ns of dollars of losses on the deals they agreed to finance in 2022,=E2=80=
=9D which =E2=80=9Climited [their] interest in extending new loans=E2=80=9D=
 for a while. The public syndicated loan market is a fairly mark-to-market =
world these days,<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" style=3D"=
color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px;=
 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; backgr=
